node.text:
Post by: @cigar.joy

As the name implies, the Joya de Nicaragua brand is most famous for making Nicaraguan puros. The Antaño is comprised of a Nicaraguan-grown Habano Criollo wrapper and Nicaraguan Habana binder and filler. 

This week’s cigar is from @cigarshack.ca

There’s going to be a new cigar next week, why not make it yours? If you’re a producer or purveyor, message me about collaborations.
